If you plan to use vmware on the machine you are connection to,
edit the ~/.vmware/preferences file and add the following line:
xkeymap.usekeycodeMap = "TRUE"

The solution was found on:
http://www.redhat.com/archives/fedora-list/2004-May/msg07383.html
===========================================================================
